text: Sen. Loeffler on whether she’s reached out to minority communities “to hear their issues and what they’re thinking”: “Absolutely, I have built my career based on bringing folks together to lift everyone up. That’s what I’ve done from Day One.” https://t.co/GiaEmSvXFo https://t.co/7Zpb5K8reI
